{
  "texts": [
    "Specifically, we used corn and soybean fractions from CDL and CSDL data (Fig.",
    "S13a) to exclusively identify corn and soybean agroecosystems (total fraction > 0.5).",
    "This alignment with our model's current training scope helped reduce the mixed pixel effect resulting from inputing remotely sensed GPP data from other ecosystems.",
    "The SoilGrids SOC stock (Fig.",
    "S13b) was derived from organic carbon density (OCD) in each layer of the 200-cm soil depth at a 250-m resolution 71."
  ]
}